    <div class="policy">

<h1 style="text-align:center">Hover Us Privacy Policy</h1>

<h4 style="text-align:center">Last Updated: July 30<sup>th</sup>, 2018</h4>
<section id="privacy-information-we-collect">
    <h3>What information do we collect?</h3>
    <p>We collect information from you when you visit this site, place an order, give us your email address, log into Facebook or Google to post.</p>
</section>

<section id="privacy-information-use">
    <h3>What do we use your information for?</h3>
    <p>Any of the information we collect from you may be used in the following ways:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>To improve our website. We continually strive to improve our website offerings based on the information and feedback we receive from you.</li>
        <li>To improve customer service. Your information helps us to more effectively respond to your customer service requests and support needs.</li>
        <li>To process transactions.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>Your information will not be sold, exchanged, transferred, or given to any other company for any reason whatsoever, without your consent, other than for the express purpose of delivering a purchased product.</p>
    
    <p>Any email address you provide, may be used to send you information and updates pertaining to your order, in addition to receiving occasional (not often) Hover Us news, updates, related product or service information.</p>
    
    <p><strong>Note:</strong> If at any time you would like to unsubscribe from receiving emails, just reply and say so, or use the Unsubscribe link.</p>
</section>

<section id="privacy-protection">
    <h3>How do we protect your information?</h3>
    <p>We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information.</p>
    <p>This site uses https. All supplied information is transmitted via Secure Socket Layer (SSL) technology and sensitive data (email address) is encrypted into our Database to be only accessed by us, for business purposes.</p>
    <p>The servers are located in the USA, very happy with <a href="http://www.a2hosting.com?aid=HoverUs">A2 Hosting</a>, and they would have access subject to their policies. No third parties are given access to our hosting.</p>
    <p>The code is open source and on <a href="https://github.com/Hover-Us/">Github</a>.</p>
</section>

<section id="privacy-cookies">
    <h3>Do we use cookies?</h3>
    <p>We respect your DNT setting shown below. We may try to use cookies to help us remember and understand and save your preferences for future visits. We do not share this data.</p>
    <p>You can block the use of cookies with your browser. If you do, you may still use our site, but your ability to use some features or areas of our site may be limited.</p>
    <p>We use Google Analytics as well as Google Analytics for Display Advertising. Google Analytics collects information and reports website trends without identifying individual visitors. Google Analytics uses its own cookie to track visitor interactions. Google, Facebook and Youtube scripts on this site might allow their cookies to track you subject to their policies.</p>
</section>

<section id="privacy-disclose-third-party">
    <h3>Do we disclose any information to outside parties?</h3>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer to outside parties your personally identifiable information. This does not include trusted third parties who assist us in servicing you, so long as those parties agree to keep this information confidential. We may also release your information when we believe release is appropriate to comply with the law, enforce our site policies, or protect ours or others rights, property, or safety. However, non-personally identifiable visitor information may be provided to other parties for showing off, marketing, or other uses.</p>
</section>

<section id="privacy-third-party-links">
    <h3>Third party links</h3>
    <p>We may include or offer third party products or services on our website. These third party sites have separate and independent privacy policies. We therefore have no responsibility or liability for the content and activities of these linked sites. Nonetheless, we seek to protect the integrity of our site and welcome any feedback about these sites.</p>
    <p>We do not have 3<sup>rd</sup> party tracking pixels or device finger printing.</p>
</section>

<section id="privacy-california">
    <h3>California Online Privacy Protection Act Compliance</h3>
    <p>Hover Us is located in California and tries hard to follow all applicable laws. We will not distribute your personal information to outside parties without your consent. If you want to see what infomation we have about you, and to remove it or make changes, send an email to privacy@hover.us and we will work with you.</p>
</section>

<section id="privacy-coppa-complicance">
    <h3>Children's Online Privacy Protection Act Compliance</h3>
    <p>We are in compliance with the requirements of COPPA (Children's Online Privacy Protection Act), we do not collect any information from anyone under 13 years of age. Our website, products and services are all directed to people who are at least 13 years old or older.</p>
</section>
        
<section id="privacy-dnt">
    <h3>Do Not Track (<b>DNT</b>)</h3>
    <p>We respect the Do Not Track flag. Your browser shows your Do Not Track flag is <span id="dnt"></span>.</p>
    <script>   
            document.getElementById('dnt').innerHTML = (window.doNotTrack||navigator.doNotTrack) ? "On" : "Off or not set";
</script>
    <p>We link to scripts from 3<sup>rd</sup> parties like Google, Youtube and/or Facebook. Please understand those companies policies as we will not try to enforce DNT for them.</p>
</section>

<section id="privacy-consent">
    <h3>Your Consent</h3>
    <p>By using our site, you consent to this privacy policy.</p>
</section>

<section id="privacy-changes">
    <h3>Changes to our Privacy Policy</h3>
    <p>If we make a change to this privacy policy, we will post those changes on this page, and and change the Last Updated date up top.</p>
</section>

<section id="privacy-contact-us">
    <h3>Contacting Us</h3>
    <p>If there are any questions regarding this privacy policy, we know who you are because we track everything. J/K email privacy@hover.us.</p>

</section>
